milestones.description: Dennis Amiss has become the top scorer for ENG in ODIs with 613 runs, going past Fletcher's 599
Zulfiqar Ali has become the top wicket-taker for E&CA in ODIs with 4 wickets, going past Mehmood Quaraishy's 1
Dennis Amiss has become the top scorer in ODIs with 613 runs, going past Fletcher's 599
Parbhu Nana has broken the record for most catches (2) in ODIs for E&CA, going past Ramesh Sethi's 1
Frasat Ali has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for E&CA, going past Harilal Shah
Dennis Amiss and Barry Wood's 158-run partnership is ENG's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 96 between Geoff Boycott and Dennis Amiss
Walusimbi and Jawahir Shah's 8-run partnership is E&CA's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 4 between Frasat Ali and Shiraz Sumar
Zulfiqar Ali and Parbhu Nana's 9-run partnership is E&CA's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 2 between Mehmood Quaraishy and Parbhu Nana
Parbhu Nana and Don Pringle's 6-run partnership is E&CA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 4 between Zulfiqar Ali and Don Pringle
